Café Website

Project Overview

This project is a simple, responsive café website created as a beginner exercise in HTML and CSS. It demonstrates foundational skills in web design, focusing on structure, styling, and layout to create a clean and inviting user experience.

Features

Home Page: Welcomes visitors with an overview of the café and its offerings.

Menu Section: Lists available food and beverages with brief descriptions.
Contact Section: Provides café contact details for easy accessibility.
Responsive Design: Optimized for various screen sizes, ensuring a seamless experience on both desktop and mobile.
Technologies Used

HTML: For structuring the content and layout.
CSS: For styling and visual design, including responsive adjustments for mobile users.
